#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kdiamond.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KDiamond is a single player puzzle game. The object of the game is to build "
"lines of three similar diamonds."
msgstr ""
"KDiament jest grą z puzzlami dla jednego gracza. Celem gry jest tworzenie "
"rzędów trzech podobnych diamentów."

